| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2670 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1c58320a-7f1d-5cfd-8bed-d6f49e91965a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
